{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/string-quotes/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/number-leading-zero/","description":"number-no-trailing-zeros 禁止数量的尾随零。 命令行中的 --fix 选项可以自动修复此规则报告的一些问题。 选项 true 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规：","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"number-no-trailing-zeros\"><a href=\"#number-no-trailing-zeros\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>number-no-trailing-zeros</h1>\n<p>禁止数量的尾随零。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5000px</span>; <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">bottom</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.0px</span>; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**         ↑                ↑\n *              这些尾随零 */</span></code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"../../../../user-guide/cli/#%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF\">命令行</a>中的 <code>--fix</code> 选项可以自动修复此规则报告的一些问题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.0px</span> }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.01000px</span> }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.01px</span> }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/number-no-trailing-zeros.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/number-no-trailing-zeros/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/number-no-trailing-zeros/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/number-no-trailing-zeros/index.html.0d395295143cb7d89b133287c396dd6e.json"}